ZH: 宫廷是皇帝和皇后以及其他贵族的居住场所。
EN: The palace is the residence of the emperor, empress, and other nobles.

ZH: 他们在宫廷举行了一场盛大的宴会。
EN: They held a grand banquet in the palace.

ZH: 宫廷里有许多美丽的花园和池塘。
EN: There are many beautiful gardens and ponds in the palace.

ZH: 宫廷内有许多宫女和太监。
EN: There are many palace maids and eunuchs in the palace.

ZH: 这座宫廷具有悠久的历史和丰富的文化。
EN: This palace has a long history and rich culture.

ZH: 很多人向宫廷进贡。
EN: Many people pay tribute to the palace.

ZH: 这幅画描绘了宫廷的生活场景。
EN: This painting depicts the scenes of palace life.

ZH: 宫廷文化有着独特的魅力和风格。
EN: Palace culture has unique charm and style.

ZH: 这段音乐是宫廷乐队演奏的。
EN: This piece of music is performed by the palace orchestra.

ZH: 宫廷里的壁画是非常漂亮的。
EN: The murals in the palace are very beautiful.

ZH: 宫廷里有许多古代文物和艺术品。
EN: There are many ancient relics and artworks in the palace.

ZH: 宫廷的礼仪非常繁琐而庄重。
EN: The ceremonial rituals in the palace are very elaborate and solemn.

ZH: 昔日的宫廷气氛使人感到肃然起敬。
EN: The atmosphere of the former palace is awe-inspiring.

ZH: 宫廷的建筑风格很独特且雄伟壮观。
EN: The architectural style of the palace is unique and magnificent.

ZH: 皇后住在宫廷的后宫。
EN: The empress lives in the harem of the palace.

ZH: 宫廷里的宴席上供应着各种美味的食物。
EN: Various delicious foods are served at the banquets in the palace.

ZH: 宫廷中流传着许多神秘的传说和故事。
EN: There are many mysterious legends and stories circulating in the palace.

ZH: 宫廷服饰是华丽而精致的。
EN: The costumes in the palace are gorgeous and exquisite.

ZH: 宫廷内进行了一场盛大的庆典活动。
EN: A grand celebration was held in the palace.

ZH: 宫廷举办了一次绚丽多彩的文化艺术展览。
EN: A splendid cultural and art exhibition was held in the palace.
